Options for leaving Azerbaijan are becoming increasingly limited. If you wish to leave Azerbaijan you should make arrangements to do so as soon as possible.
Tickets for Azerbaijan Airlines (AZAL) flights between London and Baku, departing before June cannot be purchased online. British Nationals based in Baku can purchase tickets at Silk Way Travel Office, 126A Nizami Street, Baku or by calling +994 70 437 1100. British Nationals based in the UK can purchase tickets by calling +44 1414 160 888 or by emailing london@azal.uk.
Further information
See additional advice on making travel plans to return to the UK, or what to do if you cannot depart immediately.
